olitics deaf citizens’ need kept important decision involve people”mr di maio compared yellow vest movement — sprang opposition fuel tax increase grew encompass protest economic condition — political movement offered use party’s web platformbut meeting tuesday wa apparently step farmr di maio alessandro di battista many consider party’s leaderinwaiting posted picture social medium page meeting near paris christophe chalencon organizer yellow vest movement south france ha called civil war“this picture beautiful meeting first many come talked country social right environment direct democracy” mr di maio said post “the wind change ha crossed alps”the french statement foreign ministry denounced meeting “an additional unacceptable provocation” “violated respect owed democratic choice made allied friendly nation”the french considered support yellow vest direct attack government promoted oftenviolent street opposition movement threatening country’s stability“if think deputy prime minister country go paris suburb meet guy whose movement considered criminal ha broken window setting paris fire it’s dramatically stupid movement” tocci saidthe italian populist french official said talented capturing rancor country political benefit trying capitalize france’s unrest benefit previously targeted bureaucrat brussels leader berlinsome italian attack considered simply bizarre french mr di maio recently tried cast french root cause migration issue alleging systematically impoverished former colony printing backing common currency cfa franc‘‘if europe want bit courage need face issue africa’s decolonization’’ said ‘‘i tired speaking consequence immigration want start discussing causes”he added “the european union sanction france european country impoverishing africa”french official said currency accusation wa pure invention pointed many country migrant italy often came eritrea somalia fact former italian colony site italian atrocitieson jan 22 french government summoned italy’s ambassa